{"tid":1297444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"七旬陳伯絕食逾120小時　市民憂心盼政府盡快聽訴求","createTime":"2019-07-08T15:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T17:25:24.000Z","uid":20933,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f1061f23335f59913c4e96c4ad250109d24b11b3","tid":1297444,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190708/s00001/33d24bfba6bb604861a096682746023b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190708%2Fs00001%2F33d24bfba6bb604861a096682746023b.jpg&h=50afbbd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n七旬陳伯（右）在海富中心絕食逾120小時，現場有不少年輕人圍着他聊天。（蘇智鑫攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190708/s00001/33d2929aa96da9b908d43c49f10a3541.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190708%2Fs00001%2F33d2929aa96da9b908d43c49f10a3541.jpg&h=bedeb747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳伯說，「不到臨界點仍會堅持」。（蘇智鑫攝）"},{"pid":"8719a3a9a7973311b1869b81a3527294ad20500c","tid":1297444,"uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:44:18.000Z","msg":"好鄰舍北區教會傳道人陳凱興上周三（3日）發起絕食抗議，反對《逃犯條例》修訂，目前累計8人參加。年紀最大參加者、73歲的陳伯至今已絕食逾120小時，經醫護檢查，目前血壓及血糖等指數仍維持正常，現場有不少年輕人圍着陳伯聊天，齊聲勸喻陳伯注意身體情況，適時停止絕食行動，但陳伯說「不到臨界點仍會堅持」。<br />\n<br />\n絕食行動參加者聚集在金鐘海富中心對出天橋地下。市民陳先生及朱小姐說，見到連登討論區有網民表示陳伯身體情況不理想，感到憂心。他們稱，本來頗擔心陳伯身體狀况，但見到陳伯仍有精神與人聊天便放心，「希望政府盡快聆聽到市民訴求，讓陳伯不用那麼辛苦」。<br />\n<br />\n另一名絕食參加者、退休社工梁先生已絕食超過100小時，他自言不擔心身體情況，但憂心社會矛盾情緒，「現場很多人跟我說，要顧自己身體，因為政府無論如何也不會改變。整個社會都是不信任，叫香港日後如何走下去，如何修補？」<br />\n<br />\n絕食行動發起人陳凱興接受《明報》查詢時說，至今暫有8名參加者，患有乳癌的張女士已完成絕食、時數達98小時；其餘7人仍然繼續，各人絕食時數至今介乎20至120多個小時不等。"},{"pid":"4ebd80e0b703c5cbe24e2ed849bf8ccc61ded852","tid":1297444,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:44:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190708/s00001/1562596206878/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190708%2Fs00001%2F1562596206878%2F&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=024557af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190708%2Fs00001%2F1562596206878%2F&h=35c61a2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190708/s00001/1562596206878/</a>"},{"pid":"6a2c9d6e568d4edde6d3ea1244a3fe626f7d4e40","tid":1297444,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b615f93791f4745dfed3c5247643e1845bf6d9","tid":1297444,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d33410b3617a2c2c5ea585cc2233a52b2955d2","tid":1297444,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqpj7H2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmqpj7H2.gif&h=de954cf5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oB5zb9J.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoB5zb9J.gif&h=442e1d2d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gdV3PWo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgdV3PWo.gif&h=df146aa0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VAGiDPK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVAGiDPK.gif&h=7d283340&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9xmVF24.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9xmVF24.gif&h=6d099938&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LuQZ7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k